    trt:deprecates <http://taxon-concept.plazi.org/id/Animalia/Amphiesma_sauteri_maximus_Li_2022>, <http://taxon-concept.plazi.org/id/Animalia/Natrix_sauteri_Li_1909>, <http://taxon-concept.plazi.org/id/Animalia/Amphiesma_sauteri_Li_1909>, <http://taxon-concept.plazi.org/id/Animalia/Hebius_sauteri_Li_1909> ;
